ta (TV series)|Nikita]]''\n| Agent Li Bai\n| Episode: \"3.0\"\n|-\n|2012\u20132019\n|''[[Arrow (TV series)|Arrow]]''\n|Yao Fei Gulong\n|Recurring role (12 episodes)\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2014\n| ''The Novice''\n| Johnny Joo\n| TV film\n|-\n| ''[[Hawaii Five-0 (2010 TV series)|Hawaii Five-0]]''\n| Fire Capt. Hank Iona\n| Episode: \"Ku I Ka Pili Koko\"\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[CSI: Cyber]]''\n| Jordan Tan\n| Episode: \"URL, Interrupted\"\n|-\n| 2015\u20132016\n| ''[[Hell on Wheels (TV series)|Hell on Wheels]]''\n| Chang\n| Recurring role (9 episodes)\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\n| ''[[Rush Hour (U.S. TV series)|Rush Hour]]''\n| Fong\n| Recurring role (2 episodes)\n|-\n| ''[[NCIS: Los Angeles]]''\n| Zhang Kiu\n| Episode: \"Black Market\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132018\n| ''[[Blood and Water (TV series)|Blood and Water]]''\n| Evan Ong\n| Recurring role (16 episodes)\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[The Expanse (TV series)|The Expanse]]''\n| Adm. Nguyen\n| Recurring role (5 episodes)\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Altered Carbon (TV series)|Altered Carbon]]''\n| O.G. Kovacs\n| Recurring role (3 episodes)\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Wu Assassins]]''\n| Uncle Six\n| Main cast\n|}\n\n===Video Games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Sleeping Dogs (video game)|Sleeping Dogs]]''\n| Raymond Mak & Pockmark Cheuk\n| Voice Roles\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Call of Duty: Black Ops II ]]''\n| General Tian Zhao\n| Voice Role and mo cap\n\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb name|id=0542677}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mann, Byron}}\n[[Category:1967 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American male film actors]]\n[[Category:American male television actors]]\n[[Category:Hong Kong emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:University of California, Los Angeles alumni]]\n[[Category:American wushu practitioners]]\n[[Category:USC Gould School of Law alumni]]\n[[Category:20th-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century American male actors]]\n[[Category:20th-century Hong Kong male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century Hong Kong male actors]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| pre-nominals       = \n| name               = Byron Mann\n| post-nominals      = \n| image              = Byron Mann 2018.jpg\n| image_upright      = \n| landscape          = <!-- yes, if wide image, otherwise leave blank -->\n| alt                = <!-- descriptive text for use by speech synthesis (text-to-speech) software -->\n| caption            = Byron Mann in July 2018, at a [[Skyscraper (2018 film)|Skyscraper]] press conference in [[Beijing]].\n| native_name        = \u6587\u5cf0\n| native_name_lang   = zh\n| pronunciation      = \n| birth_name         = <!-- only use if different from name -->\n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1967|8|13|df=yes}}\n| birth_place        = [[British Hong Kong]]\n| baptised           = <!-- will not display if birth_date is entered -->\n| disappeared_date   = <!-- {{Disappeared date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} (disappeared date then birth date) -->\n| disappeared_place  = \n| disappeared_status = \n| death_date         = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} (DEATH date then BIRTH date) -->\n| death_place        = \n| death_cause        = \n| body_discovered    = \n| resting_place      = \n| resting_place_coordinates = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LONG|type:landmark|display=inline}} -->\n| burial_place       = <!-- may be used instead of resting_place and resting_place_coordinates (displays \"Burial place\" as label) -->\n| burial_coordinates = <!-- {{coord|LAT|LONG|type:landmark|display=inline}} -->\n| monuments          = \n| residence          = [[Los Angeles]], [[California]], U.S. <br>[[Vancouver]], [[British Columbia]], Canada<ref name=scmp/> <br> Hong Kong, China<ref name=scmp/> <br> [[Beijing]], China<ref name=scmp/>\n| nationality        = \n| other_names        = \n| citizenship       